    "en": {
      "title": "The Bestia incident; The prime suspect is Bali",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Last May 30th, the main suspect who was wanted in the double murder incident that took place in Colombo-Bestian Mawatha, was shot by the police and lost his life.",
        "The police said that he died during the shooting incident that took place in Pemmulla this morning (04).",
        "The deceased, a 41-year-old man, has been identified as an associate of underworld gang member Ganemulla Sanjeeva.",
        "Police said the suspect fled the area on a motorcycle when they attempted to arrest him.",
        "Meanwhile, the suspect stopped the motorcycle and started firing at the police with a T-56 gun."
      ],
